---
// C2K.page — this very website
// Rich app-store-style detail view for the expanded project card
---

<div class="c2k-showcase">
  <div class="c2k-card">
    <div class="c2k-content">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="c2k-header">
        <span class="c2k-name text-scramble" data-text="C2K.page" data-delay="100" data-always="false">C2K.page</span>
        <span class="c2k-badge">this site</span>
      </div>
      <p class="c2k-tagline">System monitor for my life</p>
      <p class="c2k-desc">Public observability layer for a developer's entire digital system. Self-hosted Astro SSR on an OptiPlex micro, exposed via Cloudflare Tunnel. Every page is hand-crafted — no templates, no generic cards.</p>

      <!-- Mini navbar replica -->
      <div class="c2k-mini-nav">
        <div class="c2k-mini-nav-bar">
          <span class="c2k-mini-logo">C2K</span>
          <div class="c2k-mini-links">
            <span class="c2k-mini-link" data-idx="0">Home</span>
            <span class="c2k-mini-link" data-idx="1">Projects</span>
            <span class="c2k-mini-link" data-idx="2">Log</span>
            <span class="c2k-mini-link" data-idx="3">About</span>
            <span class="c2k-mini-link" data-idx="4">Lab</span>
            <div class="c2k-mini-indicator" id="c2k-mini-indicator"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Page descriptions -->
      <div class="c2k-pages">
        <div class="c2k-page-item" data-page="0">
          <div class="c2k-page-header">
            <svg class="c2k-page-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
              <path d="M4.5 4.5a5 5 0 0 1 7 0" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
              <path d="M4.5 11.5a5 5 0 0 0 7 0" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="c2k-page-name">Home</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-page-desc">Landing beacon. Text-scramble hero intro, gradient identity mark, status pulse showing the system is alive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-page-item" data-page="1">
          <div class="c2k-page-header">
            <svg class="c2k-page-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <line x1="8" y1="4" x2="4" y2="10"></line>
              <line x1="8" y1="4" x2="12" y2="10"></line>
              <line x1="4" y1="10" x2="12" y2="10"></line>
              <circle cx="8" cy="4" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
              <circle cx="4" cy="10" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span class="c2k-page-name">Projects</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-page-desc">Spatial network dashboard. Each project is a live node with 3 expansion states — metro-map routing lines show how everything connects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-page-item" data-page="2">
          <div class="c2k-page-header">
            <svg class="c2k-page-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M2 10V8" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
              <path d="M5 10V6" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
              <path d="M8 10V4" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
              <path d="M11 10V6" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
              <path d="M14 10V8" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="c2k-page-name">Log</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-page-desc">Dev activity feed. Git commits, session notes, and build events streamed from the system — what's happening and when.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-page-item" data-page="3">
          <div class="c2k-page-header">
            <svg class="c2k-page-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M3 5l4 3-4 3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              <line x1="9" y1="12" x2="13" y2="12" stroke-linecap="round"></line>
            </svg>
            <span class="c2k-page-name">About</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-page-desc">The operator behind the system. Background, stack, philosophy — why everything is built from scratch on a mini PC in the closet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-page-item" data-page="4">
          <div class="c2k-page-header">
            <svg class="c2k-page-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M6 2v4L3 12a1 1 0 001 1h8a1 1 0 001-1l-3-6V2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              <line x1="5" y1="2" x2="11" y2="2" stroke-linecap="round"></line>
              <circle cx="7" cy="10" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span class="c2k-page-name">Lab</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-page-desc">Experimental features. Interactive showcases, animation prototypes, statusline configurator — the testing ground before things go live.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key features -->
      <div class="c2k-section-label">FEATURES</div>
      <div class="c2k-features">
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">Text scramble/decode animations — characters resolve through random glyphs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">Glassmorphic design — frosted glass cards, radial vignette, SVG glow filters</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">Statusline showcase — interactive Claude Code statusline configurator</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">Feature Lab — experimental components with expand/scramble/stagger animations</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">Mobile swipe nav — pill-shaped bottom bar with animated icon states</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-feature">
          <span class="c2k-feature-dot" style="background: var(--purple);"></span>
          <span class="c2k-feature-text">3-environment deploy — production, staging, feature branches on separate ports</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- System connections -->
      <div class="c2k-section-label">SYSTEM CONNECTIONS</div>
      <div class="c2k-connections">
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-online"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">Conductor</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">CORE STACK</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">Orchestrates agent-deck sessions that build and deploy this site. Every feature starts as a conductor task.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-online"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">Agent Deck</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">AUTOMATION</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">Claude Code sessions run in managed terminals — each feature branch gets its own isolated agent workspace.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-online"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">Beads</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">AUTOMATION</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">Git-backed issue tracker. Tasks, bugs, and features for this site are tracked as beads with dependency chains.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-standby"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">OptiPlex Dashboard</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">HARDWARE</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">The host machine. CPU, memory, service health — c2k.page will pull live telemetry from the OptiPlex status API.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-online"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">Feature Lab</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">CORE STACK</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">Experimental page where new components are prototyped before promoting to production pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-connection">
          <div class="c2k-conn-header">
            <span class="c2k-conn-dot c2k-conn-online"></span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-name">Dotfiles</span>
            <span class="c2k-conn-route">CONFIG</span>
          </div>
          <p class="c2k-conn-desc">Claude settings, skills, hooks, and shell config — symlinked from dotfiles repo, synced across machines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live preview -->
      <div class="c2k-section-label">LIVE STATUS</div>
      <div class="c2k-preview">
        <div class="c2k-preview-line">
          <span class="c2k-glyph">C2K</span>
          <span class="c2k-dim">CTO, context engineer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-preview-line">
          <span class="c2k-pulse-dot"></span>
          <span class="c2k-dim">currently building</span>
          <span class="c2k-dim c2k-dots" id="c2k-dots">...</span>
        </div>
        <div class="c2k-preview-line c2k-status-line">
          <span class="c2k-status-dot"></span>
          <span class="c2k-dim">optiplex · 8 services · cpu 12%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech & footer -->
      <div class="c2k-stack">
        <span class="c2k-tech">Astro</span>
        <span class="c2k-tech">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="c2k-tech">Bun</span>
        <span class="c2k-tech">Cloudflare</span>
        <span class="c2k-tech">Tailscale</span>
        <span class="c2k-tech">Canvas</span>
      </div>

      <div class="c2k-footer">
        <span class="c2k-version">v3.2 · self-hosted SSR</span>
        <a class="c2k-link" href="https://c2k.page" target="_blank" rel="noopener">c2k.page ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  // Animate the dots in the preview
  const dots = document.getElementById('c2k-dots');
  if (dots) {
    let count = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      count = (count + 1) % 4;
      dots.textContent = '.'.repeat(count || 1);
    }, 500);
  }

  // Mini nav indicator interaction
  function initMiniNav() {
    const links = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.c2k-mini-link');
    const indicator = document.getElementById('c2k-mini-indicator');
    const pages = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.c2k-page-item');
    if (!indicator || links.length === 0) return;

    let activeIdx = 0;

    function setActive(idx: number) {
      activeIdx = idx;
      links.forEach((link, i) => {
        link.classList.toggle('active', i === idx);
      });
      pages.forEach((page, i) => {
        page.classList.toggle('highlighted', i === idx);
      });
      // Move indicator
      const target = links[idx];
      if (target) {
        indicator.style.left = `${target.offsetLeft}px`;
        indicator.style.width = `${target.offsetWidth}px`;
        indicator.style.opacity = '1';
      }
    }

    links.forEach((link) => {
      link.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
        const idx = parseInt(link.dataset.idx || '0', 10);
        setActive(idx);
      });
    });

    // Auto-cycle through nav items
    let cycleTimer: ReturnType<typeof setInterval>;
    let paused = false;

    function startCycle() {
      cycleTimer = setInterval(() => {
        if (!paused) {
          activeIdx = (activeIdx + 1) % links.length;
          setActive(activeIdx);
        }
      }, 2500);
    }

    const container = document.querySelector('.c2k-mini-nav');
    if (container) {
      container.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => { paused = true; });
      container.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
        paused = false;
      });
    }

    // Initial state
    setActive(0);
    startCycle();
  }

  initMiniNav();
</script>

<style>
  .c2k-showcase {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .c2k-card {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--text);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 0 var(--glass-highlight), var(--card-shadow);
  }

  .c2k-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Header */
  .c2k-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c2k-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--gradient-text);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .c2k-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--purple-bg);
    color: var(--purple);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .c2k-tagline {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .c2k-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Mini navbar ── */
  .c2k-mini-nav {
    background: var(--bg-overlay);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .c2k-mini-nav-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c2k-mini-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--gradient-text);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .c2k-mini-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .c2k-mini-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .c2k-mini-link.active {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .c2k-mini-link:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .c2k-mini-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--purple-bg-subtle);
    border-radius: 4px;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    transition: left 0.25s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1),
                width 0.25s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1),
                opacity 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  /* ── Page descriptions ── */
  .c2k-pages {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .c2k-page-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 0.45rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: background 0.2s ease-out, border-color 0.2s ease-out;
  }

  .c2k-page-item.highlighted {
    background: var(--purple-bg-subtle);
    border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
  }

  .c2k-page-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .c2k-page-icon {
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .c2k-page-item.highlighted .c2k-page-icon {
    color: var(--purple);
  }

  .c2k-page-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .c2k-page-item.highlighted .c2k-page-name {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .c2k-page-desc {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding-left: 1.15rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .c2k-page-item.highlighted .c2k-page-desc {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  /* ── Section labels ── */
  .c2k-section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.1rem;
  }

  /* ── Features ── */
  .c2k-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .c2k-feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .c2k-feature-dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .c2k-feature-text {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── System connections ── */
  .c2k-connections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .c2k-connection {
    background: var(--bg-overlay);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.65rem;
  }

  .c2k-conn-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .c2k-conn-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .c2k-conn-online {
    background: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 4px var(--green-glow);
  }

  .c2k-conn-standby {
    background: var(--orange);
    box-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4);
  }

  .c2k-conn-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .c2k-conn-route {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-left: auto;
    padding: 0.05rem 0.35rem;
    background: var(--bg-code);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .c2k-conn-desc {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    line-height: 1.4;
    padding-left: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* ── Live preview terminal ── */
  .c2k-preview {
    background: var(--bg-overlay);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .c2k-preview-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }

  .c2k-glyph {
    background: var(--gradient-text);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .c2k-dim {
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
  }

  .c2k-pulse-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--purple);
    animation: c2k-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .c2k-status-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @keyframes c2k-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  /* ── Tech stack ── */
  .c2k-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c2k-tech {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    background: var(--bg-code);
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  .c2k-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .c2k-version {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
  }

  .c2k-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--purple-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .c2k-link:hover {
    color: var(--purple);
  }
</style>
